nodes.text: A female Dathomirian was the oldest sister of the Dathomiri Witches Kaminne and Olianne Sihn of the Raining Leaves Clan on the planet Dathomir.
In 33 ABY, an uprising of the clan's male slaves occurred which resulted in the deaths of over two-thirds of the clan's population. Sihn's sister was among those who perished.
